Author : Thomas BERNARD

Makefile to compile and install VASM / VBCC by Volker Barthelmann

Tested on GNU/linux debian 7.11

at the moment it compiles vasmm68k_mot / vbccm68ks for +tos16 config.

$ make
$ export VBCC=/path/to/install/vbcc
$ make install

and then add to your .profile or .bashrc :
export VBCC=/path/to/install/vbcc
export PATH=${VBCC}/bin:${PATH}
